		"!ObjectScript": "res://assets/Scripts/Items/Pages/PageItemTitle.gd",
		"!ParentKey": "BanditBase_TitlePage",
		"#ObjDetails": {
			"Description": "Every ship needs a @@#Color:Red:Captain@@, and while @@#Color:Red:Bandits@@ are not necessarily ships, they do still benefit from well organized leadership.\n\n@@#Color:Red:Bandit Captains@@ earned their @@#Color:Blue:Title@@ thanks to their higher than average @@#Color:Red:Attributes@@. Naturally, they keep the best loot for themselves which means they tend to have better @@#Stat:Armor@@ and @@#Tag:HeavyWeapon:Hint:Heavy Weapons@@.\n\nThey often like to live by the motto:\n\"Carry a big stick, and use it.\"",
			"DisplayName": "Bandit Captain",
